      "index": 12,
      "text": "Darius, raise the Founding Houses on the comms. Tell them that I'm ordering them to drop. All of our companies, our entire fleet—everything we have. As always, I will lead from the front.\n\nWe're taking Coromodir, and we are doing it <i>now</i>.",
      "branches": [
