        "id": "5a8b8972623035601f001923"
      },
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Perhaps. But while my uncle holds Coromodir, he retains the illusion of legitimacy, and <i>that</i> is something I can no longer allow.\n\nThe time has come to take it from him.",
